OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC advises staff to delete
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FTikTok from work phones    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has advised staff to delete    
OL,6, TikTok from corporate phones because of
OL,7, privacy and security fears.            
OL,9,FThe BBC seems to be the first UK media 
OL,10,Forganisation to issue the guidance -   
OL,11,Fand only the second in the world after 
OL,12,FDenmark's public service broadcaster.  
OL,14,FThe BBC said it would continue to use  
OL,15,Fthe platform for editorial and         
OL,16,Fmarketing purposes for now. TikTok has 
OL,17,Fconsistently denied any wrongdoing.    
OL,19,FThe app has been banned on government  
OL,20,Fphones in the UK and elsewhere.        
